{"tw": {"1528540": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "聖妓女艾蜜莉", "steam_appid": 1528540, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18年前，樞機主教吉爾伯特由於在首都的總教會犯下了過錯，遭到教會懲罰，貶謫至偏遠的臨海城鎮‧凱納斯頓，接替離世的主教治理這裡20年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >時光飛逝，凱納斯頓變成了繁榮的貿易要鎮，而他在此處的孤兒院收養的女兒，艾蜜莉，也迎接了她的18歲生日。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >長年沒有「祝福之女」──受到愛芙洛女神欽點的代理人擔任聖女守護的城鎮，勢必將會讓這裡再度走向貧困與毀滅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觀察到艾蜜莉擁有不輸歷任聖女資質的吉爾伯特，決定讓她擔任聖女，然而，不是祝福之女的她，果不其然遭到信徒們的反對，因此他向大家約定，若她無法在這兩年內獲得認同，將會卸下聖女職位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/bae978dc953deda3cb33ebc20fb77247.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/bae978dc953deda3cb33ebc20fb77247.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/bae978dc953deda3cb33ebc20fb77247.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在吉爾伯特指導艾蜜莉成為聖女的同時，教會卻出現了入侵者！神出鬼沒的他屢次成功脫離教會的追捕，令吉爾伯特十分頭痛，他的目的究竟是什麼……？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩年時間說長不長、說短不短，兩人的相處時間也一點一滴減少，究竟艾蜜莉是否能夠突破重重困難，破除信眾「非祝福之女無法擔任聖女」的迷思，實現自己的理想呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/b4827bc31ea1a58bd52837fd19020c7d.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/b4827bc31ea1a58bd52837fd19020c7d.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/b4827bc31ea1a58bd52837fd19020c7d.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每日有三個時段，玩家將扮演凱納斯頓鎮的主教，在兩年的期限內指導與培養艾蜜莉在教會中進行各種活動，或到街上嘗試各種工作增加收入，部分行動將隨著劇情發展而開放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >累積足夠資金後，可投資擴建教會，給艾蜜莉更好的學習環境，增加學習與工作效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與艾蜜莉的互動也不可忽視，多多與她互動、維繫關係，讓她與您的關係更親密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行動後所累積的各項數值將會影響最終結局，請隨時確認她的學習計畫，完成所有任務，為她安排最好的未來吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/c9e410ec7908d602d906db92f9b3de15.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/c9e410ec7908d602d906db92f9b3de15.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/c9e410ec7908d602d906db92f9b3de15.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇30張基本CG，11組動態HCG+13組靜態HCG，包含多張差分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇遊戲文字約12萬字</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇一位主要女角，包含與主角的H以及與其他人的H劇情，可純愛通關</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇以聖女為目標的女兒養成遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇8種通常結局、2種Extra結局以及2種中途BE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/68a863b45df110600cf3050ee784c603.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/68a863b45df110600cf3050ee784c603.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/68a863b45df110600cf3050ee784c603.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.poster.avif?t=1776855273\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.webm?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528540/extras/e806da4c0372442dfe4c2f5d3dec35da.mp4?t=1776855273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18年前，樞機主教吉爾伯特由於在首都的總教會犯下了過錯，遭到教會懲罰，貶謫至偏遠的臨海城鎮‧凱納斯頓，接替離世的主教治理這裡20年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >時光飛逝，凱納斯頓變成了繁榮的貿易要鎮，